metadata.title: Sea Otter, Boat Survey Design, Bathymetry

creators.name: Wildlife Service (USFWS), Oil Spill Administration Office

metadata.description: Data Type: Mammals;  These coverages were derived from the integration of pre-existing boat survey design for sea otters with bathymetry data. Scale for the boat survey is 1:63,360 the scale for the bathymetry is unknown.
